These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, thai, colombian, american
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, mouse, horse
1. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the french##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the american is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the american is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
7. the thai is somewhere between the french and the owner of the snake##7
8. the thai and the owner of the horse have the same parity positions##9
9. the colombian and the owner of the fish have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | french | thai | colombian     | american |
| Pet           | mouse   | horse     | snake | fish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, 7up, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, chess, filmmaking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person drinking mirinda have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water     | 7up    | milk | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | fishing | chess | filmmaking      | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber, plum, cauliflower
1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
2. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
7. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person eating cucumber##8
8. the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating cucumber have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | mirinda   | tea    | sprite  |
| Food       | cucumber | cauliflower | pineapple | plum |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, mechanic, project-manager, journalist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, rock, classical
1. the fan house is the mechanic##1
2. the fan country is on the right of the fan rock##1
3. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
4. the fan classical is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
5. the fan country is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the journalist and the fan classical have the same parity positions##9
7. the project-manager is on the left or right of the engineer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | journalist | project-manager | engineer  | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | rock             | country          | classical | house    |

