.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, dubstep, indie
4 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat, guinea-pig
1. the fan dubstep is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the owner of the bird and the fan salsa have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the lizard and the fan reggae have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the fan indie##1
6. the fan reggae is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5
8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the fan salsa##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the fan indie##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | dubstep | indie  | reggae |
| Pet           | lizard   | bird     | rat | guinea-pig      |

