.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, action, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, australian, russian
1. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
4. the british and the person watching action movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching musical movies and the british have different parity positions##9
6. the australian is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
7. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the russian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | disaster | action | musical |
| Nationality   | russian        | australian    | british   | malaysian |

