The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, golf, weightlifting, badminton
1. the fan techno is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
3. the person who's sport is badminton and the fan metal have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the fan metal is not to the right of the fan rock##8
6. the fan techno is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5
7. the fan metal is somewhere to the right of the fan d&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | techno | metal         | rock     |
| Sport         | golf | badminton  | weightlifting | handball |

