.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, traveling, board-games, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, guinea-pig, pony
1. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the cat##7
2. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the owner of the dog##6
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the owner of the pony have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | traveling | writing | board-games |
| Pet     | cat     | guinea-pig     | pony     | dog    |

