.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, cabbage, kiwi, raspberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, train, boat, subway
1. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person eating peas##8
2. the person eating raspberry and the person driving the subway have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person eating cabbage is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person driving the subway##7
6. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | kiwi | peas   | cabbage | raspberry |
| Transport   | boat   | train | taxi    | subway      |

