The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, chess, writing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating mango have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | apricot | pepper | cucumber   | mango   |
| Hobby   | woodworking  | writing   | chess | sudoku |

