The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, van, scooter, quad-bike
1. the fan reggae is on the right of the fan classical##1
2. the fan classical is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
3. the fan trance and the person driving the van have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the fan trance##1
5. the fan reggae is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
