1. the person eating apple and the fan ambient have the same parity positions##9
2. the fan ambient is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
3. the person eating nectarine is somewhere between the fan classical and the fan ambient##7
4. the fan ambient is somewhere between the fan country and the person eating nectarine##7
5. the fan r&b is not the person eating pumpkin##6
6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
7. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pumpkin | nectarine | apple | papaya  |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | r&b | ambient | country |

