.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, water, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, western, musical, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
8. the person watching documentary movies and the person drinking mirinda have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching musical movies and the person drinking water have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate  | water  | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | sports | documentary      |

