3. the fisherman is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
4. the architect is not to the right of the paramedic##8
5. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the dog and the analyst have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the goldfish and the fisherman have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
