The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, photography, card-games, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is cooking have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water    | sprite | fanta | tea |
| Hobby      | card-games | cooking   | photography   | reading   |

