.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, baking, camping, writing
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is baking have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 9. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is baking have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | iced-tea        | milk   | soy-milk      |
| Hobby      | writing | camping | baking | card-games |

 